frames.caption: A group of people dressed in traditional Eastern European attire stand outside a rustic wooden building. The central figure, a young woman, wears a colorful embroidered dress and headscarf, while the others, mostly older men, wear fur hats and layered garments. The scene is set against a snowy backdrop, suggesting a cold, winter day.
